    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly a little sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells just like it did the day it left the dealership! I've babied this ride since day one, keeping it garaged and spotless. If you're looking for something that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a road trip today, you\u2019ve found it! Drop me a message if you want to come see it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
