    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey everyone! I\u2019m so excited to share this absolute gem with you. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape that it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since the day I got it\u2014it\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously cleaned, and looks virtually brand new inside and out. It drives like a dream and has been 100% reliable. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and cared for, this is definitely the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions at all\u2014I\u2019m happy to chat!",
